'''甲磺酸钡'''是一种[[化合物|化合物]]，化学式为Ba(CH<sub>3</sub>SO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>，是正交晶系的晶体<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Applied Crystallography|volume=13|issue=2|issn=0021-8898|date=1980-04-01|pages=190–190|doi=10.1107/S0021889880011831|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0021889880011831|title=Crystal data for barium methanesulphonate Ba(CH 3 SO 3 ) 2|accessdate=2021-01-08|author=Y. Garaud, F. Charbonnier, R. Faure|archive-date=2018-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603114300/http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0021889880011831|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它可由[[氧化钡|氧化钡]]（或[[氢氧化钡|氢氧化钡]]<ref name=Wang />）和[[甲磺酸|甲磺酸]]反应，重结晶后制得。<ref name=Gong>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Thermal Analysis and Calorimetry|volume=98|issue=3|language=en|issn=1388-6150|date=2009-12|pages=801–806|doi=10.1007/s10973-009-0119-z|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s10973-009-0119-z|title=Thermal decomposition of metal methanesulfonates in air|accessdate=2021-01-08|author=M. Wang, Z. G. Song, H. Jiang, H. Gong}}</ref>它和[[硫酸|硫酸]]反应，生成[[甲磺酸|甲磺酸]]和[[硫酸钡|硫酸钡]]。<ref name=Wang>Wang, Zhijun(汪志君). Purification method of methanesulfonic acid(一种甲基磺酸的提纯方法). 2017. CN 106748907 A.</ref>它的热分解产物是硫酸钡。<ref name=Gong />

